  ASD Research Activities
     __________________________________________________________________

   Airborne Research Programs
     * Light Detection and Ranging
     * Lidar Atmospheric Sensing Experiment

   Spaceborne Research Programs
     * Clouds and the Earth's Radiant Energy System (CERES)
     * Earth Radiation Budget Experiment (ERBE)
     * Halogen Occultation Experiment (HALOE) server
     * Lidar-In-space Technology Experiment (LITE)
     * Pathfinder Instrument for Cloud and Aerosol Spaceborne Observations
       - Climatologie Etendue des Nuages et des Aerosols (ESSP3-CENA)
     * Sounding of the Atmosphere using Broadband Emission Radiometry
       (SABER)
     * Stratospheric Aerosol and Gas Experiment (SAGE)II
     * Statospheric Aerosol and Gas Experiment III (SAGE III)

   Multi-Platform Research Programs
     * First ISCCP Regional Experiment (FIRE)
     * Global Tropospheric Experiment (GTE)

   Large-Scale Atmospheric Studies
     * Atmospheric Chemistry Programs
     * Atmospheric Spectroscopic Research Programs
     * Global Atmospheric Modeling
     * Interactive Modeling Project for Atmospheric Chemistry and
       Transport (IMPACT)

   Biomass Burning and Global Change
     * Biomass Burning and Global Change
